channel.title: RuneWings317 ~ Delta ~ Now available for download!
channel.description:
1000 some votes and no posts? Please, lets do better than that or I'll remove.
Hey guys! Heres my last server I had. I moved on to Project Insanity. So here is the information!
Read First: I do not give permission for people to post on other sites. If found on other sites, even if you give me credits, I will remove the download links and the post. I do not give people the rights to leach this. If found on other sites under your name with nothing important changed, I will come after you. This is a delta source, thus, under common sense, only codes that have to do with delta will work. The original source was made by Lost Valentino.
Credits: Me (XLdarkwingLX), JJ, Martino, Devon, Lost Valentino and other TuTs Other Info: I have an exe file for running on a windows 7 computer. Original Source: Corby Xevolution (Something like that)
Downloads! Client ~ 533 downloads Server ~ 305
What to look forward to in 2nd release: ~Staff Zone ~Editing the client a lot ~More commands ~Fixing more bugs ~Working on canoes
What I did: ~Made an awesome new home ~Added monsters/drops that he didn't add ~Fixed skillcape emotes ~Made an awesome new skilling zone ~A new minigame made by me ~Fixed some special attacks
And lots lots more!
Features: ~Working Skill Cape Emotes ~Custom home, skilling area and training area! ~Renamed NPCs ~Minigames (My custom mummy one, assault, pest control and more!) ~Working Tele Other (Thanks to deathchaos) ~Canoe system 40% (By me) ~Barbarian Agility Course 95% (by me) ~New areas released And LOTS LOTS MORE!
